<span class="postbody">Im in a top guild on TM.  I like the pepole and have a good time with them.  The issue I have is that the leadership thinks all 2HB should go to MNKs.   I know from reading here than 2hb can be powerful for BST with the new ratios etc., but how do i convince them? The number one guild on the server gives BSTs the same chance as MNKs so i know there is logic behind it. Here is what I have so far. 
<br />

<br />
1. 2hb is golden when DSs are present on mobs
<br />
2. 2hb is great in POP due to enrage
<br />
3. 2hb allows us to cast without losing dps.
<br />

<br />

<br />
What else can you think of?  What kinda dps diff would most upper 2hb do for us versus MNKs?  (ie emp staff, REBB, fire staff....)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Thanks for your help.... glad to see the boards back up <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
