<span class="postbody">I don't see how there could be so many monks in your guild that it would be impossible for you to get a high end 2hb even with the monks getting first dibs.  They will get more out of it than you will since all of their damage comes from melee, so I don't see anything really wrong with that.  It shouldn't take long for you to get a shot at one, each monk only needs one 2hb.  The top 3 or so 2hbs in the game hardly have any dps difference so it's not worth getting more than 1.
<br />

<br />
-Jurayn Neutered - Lanys</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
